data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with a 2-car garage and a convenient drive-up driveway. As you step inside the basement, you'll be greeted by a beautiful home theater, perfect for movie nights with family and friends. The spacious master suite features an en-suite bathroom for added privacy and luxury.    This home boasts a big backyard, ideal for hosting family gatherings and outdoor activities. With 4 floors of living space, there is plenty of room for everyone to enjoy. This is a perfect home for those looking for both comfort and entertainment. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours!
